---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About Nick Reef — Full-Stack Developer | OpsHQ Digital"
  description="10+ years building production software. Direct access to the developer — no middlemen, no project managers. Seattle, WA."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-950 to-navy-800 text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">You Deserve a Developer Who Actually Picks Up the Phone</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">OpsHQ Digital is a one-developer technology practice built on a simple idea: you should be able to call the person building your system and get a straight answer.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bio -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>I'm Nick Reef, the founder and sole developer behind OpsHQ Digital.</p>
        <p>Here's what I've learned in 10+ years of building software: <strong class="text-navy-950">the best technology is the kind you don't have to think about.</strong> You check one email in the morning and know what's happening. Leads get followed up automatically. Payments are tracked without spreadsheets. Your website actually brings in customers.</p>
        <p>That's what I build — production software that makes business owners' lives easier. CRM systems, AI agents, websites, and cloud infrastructure. Not prototypes. Not demos. Systems that handle real customers, real money, and real deadlines.</p>
        <p>The right question isn't "what framework should we use?" It's <strong class="text-navy-950">"what's the simplest thing that solves your problem and doesn't break at 2 AM?"</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why OpsHQ -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-12 text-center">Our Approach</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">📞</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">Direct Access</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">When you hire OpsHQ Digital, you work directly with the person writing the code. No project managers, no handoffs, no "I'll have to check with the team."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🛡️</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">Battle-Tested Solutions</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Every system ships with monitoring, security, automated deployments, and documentation. "It works on my machine" isn't a deployment strategy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-200 text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">💲</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">Transparent Pricing</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Fixed-price quotes after the discovery call. No hourly billing surprises, no scope creep. Your technology bill should be predictable and boring.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technology Partners -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-8">Technology Partners</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 text-slate-500">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-3xl">☁️</span>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium">Microsoft Azure</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-3xl">🛡️</span>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium">Cloudflare</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-3xl">💻</span>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium">GitHub</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Need -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-6">What We Need From You</h2>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4"><strong class="text-navy-950">Your part is simple.</strong> We handle the technical heavy lifting — you provide the business knowledge.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600">
          <li>• <strong>1-2 hours</strong> on the initial discovery call and follow-up questions</li>
          <li>• <strong>30 minutes/week</strong> reviewing progress and giving feedback during the build</li>
          <li>• <strong>Access</strong> to your existing tools/systems we'll be connecting to</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4">That's it. No technical skills required. No homework assignments. We do the building — you keep running your business.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-950 to-navy-800 text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Looking for a Technical Partner — Not Just a Vendor?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">I take on a limited number of clients so I can give each one my full attention. Let's have a conversation.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors min-h-[44px] text-lg">
        Request a Free Discovery Call
      </a>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-6">
        Or email <a href="mailto:nick@opshqdigital.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline">nick@opshqdigital.com</a>
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-400">
        <a href="/services/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Our Services →</a>
        <a href="/services/crm/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">CRM Development →</a>
        <a href="/services/ai/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">AI Automation →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
